English:

alias:int_server.1024_ciph.tier5.phys_ops/PDeckerC085.flagged

Decker,

Why is it that every terminal and control screen I have to look at in this shit hole tries to burn my retinas to
a crisp? Is Santonian trying to make us forget about the real sun? For the love of god can you see if
there's a way to turn the brightness down on these stupid screens?

Igor.
